---
title: Breakfast Bacon Quesadilla Stacks with Poblano Hash Browns, Avocado, and Bacon
description: The breakfast quesadilla is pretty under-the-radar in the scope of breakfast foods, outshone by its more popular cousins the breakfast taco and breakfast burrito. But considering that quesadillas are really just a grilled cheese disguised in a tortilla, they might be the most breakfast-worthy of all. This one is packed with spicy and savory elements, from a potato poblano hash to slices of crispy, mouthwatering bacon.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w18-breakfast-dc4342a0.jpg
